msg":"隻大和號屌打"},{"pid":"463c92a4bddaeaffdbfcf5ec54391be7b9135165","tid":1661261,"uid":312242,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"唔係崔支那嘅戰力，但而家航空母艦科技係好唔同。 <br />\n<br />\n大日本帝國海軍嘅機動部隊係好強大但係遼寧號每一架嘅sukhoi射一發防船導彈啲空母都死呀。<br />\n<br />\n睇下日軍空母嘅攻擊力,都係得啲濕鳩A6M零戰做CAP close air patrol,佢最勁嗰啲攻擊機D4Y都係可以盛載dumb bombs攻擊程度好似橡筋vs狙擊槍一樣。<br />\n<br />\n除非你無啦啦閃己架戰艦喺遼寧號隔離咁嗰個遼寧號一定死。空母根據過往經驗好似一場battle of samar 戰爭, 係近距離唔夠戰艦來的"},{"pid":"1766656d5239669aa27fcfa4b582433ddf19fb6f","tid":1661261,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"遼寧號係五十年代技術，話唔定不相伯仲"},{"pid":"e719fdb415971c7cea7dcefe218e058dcb6976b1","tid":1661261,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1766656d5239669aa27fcfa4b582433ddf19fb6f","tid":1661261,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"遼寧號係五十年代技術，話唔定不相伯仲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"個船嘅hull好舊,但係裝備可以modernize，嗰啲咁嘅sukhoi飛機唔算舊嘢。"},{"pid":"e5e34b1e4c56dcf9fb393cb4cfbc920273eb96fc","tid":1661261,"uid":41853,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"一定唔夠啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都係想聽依句姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日係到自欺欺人係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92007030d0d891e66e8ddbfac771f7625f15af32","tid":1661261,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f5e35ef4d4953a7b4e4958afb1b038fb72edaa","tid":1661261,"uid":101051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"認真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴射戰機VS螺旋戰機<br />\n大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa